          <p>Filmist 2.5 released this week, with improvements made to Portra 800, Kodachrome 64, Classic Neg, and more, and a new film type, Fuji Instant 800 (used above).</p>
          <p>There's also sales happening. Filmist is currently marked down to celebrate the new release, and Seim's Summer sale is on: use the code <strong>SMR25</strong> to save 25% storewide. If you miss the sale, though ...
          <hr />
