					<h2>Until next time ...</h2>
          <p>That's a wrap for now. No other links to share, and no music pick this edition.</p>
          <p>Now that the shop move is complete, we can hopefully get back to our usual cadence of product updates, and you'll hear from us again when the next version of Backlight is available.</p>
